Carlo Rota https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlo_Rota 0 Carlo Rota (born 17 April 1961) is an English-born Canadian actor, best known to Canadian audiences for his role on Little Mosque on the Prairie and to international audiences as systems analyst Morris O'Brian on the FOX series 24. He also has a co-starring role as Emilio Solano in Jane the Virgin.
